column31: - **On Previous Row Total / Amount** (for cumulative taxes or charges). If you select this option, the tax will be applied as a percentage of the previous row (in the tax table) amount or total.
column37: 2. Account Head: The Account ledger under which this tax will be booked
column40: 3. Cost Center: If the tax / charge is an income (like shipping) or expense it needs to be booked against a Cost Center.
